>Additional timed-based and collectathon challenges that reward replays </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute, cuddly, and made for all ages and skill levels</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803840/extras/f43997a69f6547ac7498f47137845f1a.poster.avif?t=1730232875\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803840/extras/f43997a69f6547ac7498f47137845f1a.webm?t=1730232875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803840/extras/f43997a69f6547ac7498f47137845f1a.mp4?t=1730232875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
